queries.query:
from(bucket: "capacity_data")
  |> range(start: 0)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "capacities") //Filter by capacities measurement
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r.product_name == "Washing Powder") //Filter by product name tag
  |> last()  //Only get last submission
